</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq">---
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq">## . Project Overview
</span><span class="x1lliihq">The Smart Parking System is an automated solution developed using Arduino UNO and simulated in Tinkercad. It efficiently manages parking spaces by detecting vehicles using ultrasonic sensors and controlling entry and exit gates using servo motors. The system provides real-time parking status through an OLED display and LED indicators, reducing manual effort and improving parking efficiency.
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq">---
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq">## . Key Features
