ltr" class="x1f6kntn xjb2p0i x8r4c90 xo1l8bm x1ic7a3i x12xpedu _ao3e _aupe copyable-text" style="min-height: 0px;"><span class="x1lliihq">Here’s a clear, complete working principle of your project from start to finish, including IoT with Blynk IoT and simulation in Wokwi. You can use this directly in your record + viva.
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq">---
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq"><img crossorigin="anonymous" alt="🚦" draggable="false" data-testid="selectable-text" class="b90 emoji wa  _ao3e _aupe copyable-text" data-plain-text="🚦" tabindex="-1" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" style="background-position: -80px -80px;"> WORKING PRINCIPLE
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq">IoT-Based Smart Traffic Control with Emergency Override
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq">---
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq"><img crossorigin="anonymous" alt="🔹" draggable="false" data-testid="selectable-text" class="b78 emoji wa  _ao3e _aupe copyable-text" data-plain-text="🔹" tabindex="-1" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" style="background-position: 0px 0px;"> 1. System Overview
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq">This system is designed to:
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq">Automatically control traffic signals
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq">Adjust signal timing based on traffic density
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq">Provide priority to emergency vehicles using IoT
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq">The system uses an ESP32 microcontroller, which connects to the internet and communicates with the Blynk cloud.
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
</span><span class="x1lliihq">---
</span><span class="x1lliihq">
